^n594 tathā arūpapaṭisandhiyā ca mahaggatabhūtaṃ paññattibhūtañca kammanimittameva yathārahamārammaṇaṃ hoti।
^n asaññasattānaṃ pana jīvitanavakameva paṭisandhibhāvena patiṭṭhāti,
 tasmā te rūpapaṭisandhikā nāma।
^n arūpā arūpapaṭisandhikā।
^n sesā rūpārūpapaṭisandhikā।
paṭisandhi	^n595 āruppacutiyā honti, heṭṭhimāruppavajjitā।
^n^sz paramāruppasandhī ca, tathā kāmatihetukā॥
^n^sz rūpāvacaracutiyā, aheturahitā siyuṃ।
^n^sz sabbā kāmatihetumhā, kāmesveva panetarā॥
^n ^end ayamettha cutipaṭisandhikkamo।
^n596 iccevaṃ gahitapaṭisandhikānaṃ pana paṭisandhinirodhānantarato pabhuti tamevārammaṇamārabbha tadeva cittaṃ yāva cuticittuppādā asati vīthicittuppāde
 bhavassa aṅgabhāvena bhavaṅgasantatisaṅkhātaṃ mānasaṃ abbocchinnaṃ nadīsoto viya pavattati।
^n597 pariyosāne ca cavanavasena cuticittaṃ hutvā nirujjhati।
^n598 tato parañ0ca paṭisandhādayo rathacakkamiva yathākkamaṃ eva parivattantā pavattanti।
^n599^n600 paṭisandhibhavaṅgavīthiyo, cuticeha tathā bhavantare।
^n^sz puna sandhi bhavaṅgamiccayaṃ, parivattati cittasantati॥
^n^sz paṭisaṅkhāyapanetamaddhuvaṃ, adhigantvā padamaccutaṃ budhā।
^n^sz susamucchinnasinehabandhanā, samamessanti cirāya subbatā॥
^n ^end iti abhidhammatthasaṅgahe vīthimuttasaṅgahavibhāgo nāma
^n ^end pañcamo paricchedo।
rūpa	^ck#aas6(6. rūpaparicchedo)^n601 ettāvatā vibhattā hi, sappabhedappavattikā।
^n^sz cittacetasikā dhammā, rūpaṃ dāni pavuccati॥
^n602 samuddesā vibhāgā ca, samuṭṭhānā kalāpato।
^n^sz pavattikkamato ceti, pañcadhā tattha saṅgaho॥
^h(rūpasamuddeso)^n603 cattāri mahā0bhūtāni, catunnañ0ca mahā0bhūtānaṃ upādāyarūpanti
 ^b(duvidhampetaṃ rūpaṃ) ekādasavidhena saṅgahaṃ gacchati।
^n604 kathaṃ? pathavī0dhātu āpo0dhātu tejo0dhātu vāyo0dhātu ^b(bhūtarūpaṃ) nāma।
^n605 cakkhu sotaṃ ghānaṃ jivhā kāyo ^b(pasādarūpaṃ) nāma।
^n606 rūpaṃ saddo gandho raso āpodhātuvivajjitaṃ bhūtattayasaṅkhātaṃ phoṭṭhabbaṃ ^b(gocararūpaṃ) nāma।
^n607 itthattaṃ purisattaṃ ^b(bhāvarūpaṃ) nāma।
^n608 hadayavatthu ^b(hadayarūpaṃ) nāma।
^n609 jīvitindriyaṃ ^b(jīvitarūpaṃ) nāma।
^n610 kabaḷīkāro āhāro ^b(āhārarūpaṃ) nāma।
^n611 iti ca aṭṭhārasavidhampetaṃ rūpaṃ sabhāvarūpaṃ salakkhaṇarūpaṃ nipphannarūpaṃ rūparūpaṃ sammasanarūpanti ca saṅgahaṃ gacchati।
paricchedarūpaṃ	^n612 ākāsa0dhātu ^b(paricchedarūpaṃ) nāma।
^n613 kāyaviññatti vacīviññatti ^b(viññattirūpaṃ) nāma।
^n614 rūpassa lahutā mudutā kammaññatā viññattidvayaṃ ^b(vikārarūpaṃ) nāma।
^n615 rūpassa upacayo santati jaratā aniccatā ^b(lakkhaṇarūpaṃ) nāma।
^n616 jātirūpameva panettha upacayasantatināmena pavuccatī0ti
 ekādasavidhampetaṃ rūpaṃ aṭṭhavīsatividhaṃ hoti sarūpavasena।
^n617 kathaṃ –
^n^sz bhūtappasādavisayā, bhāvo hadayamiccapi।
^n^sz jīvitāhārarūpehi, aṭṭhārasavidhaṃ tathā॥
^n^sz paricchedo ca viññatti, vikāro lakkhaṇanti ca।
^n^sz anipphannā dasa ceti, aṭṭhavīsavidhaṃ bhave॥
^n ^end ayamettha rūpasamuddeso।
rūpavibhāgo	^h(rūpavibhāgo)^n618 sabbañ0ca panetaṃ rūpaṃ ahetukaṃ sappaccayaṃ sāsavaṃ saṅkhataṃ lokiyaṃ kāmāvacaraṃ anārammaṇaṃ appahātabbamevāti ekavidhampi ajjhattikabāhirādivasena bahudhā bhedaṃ gacchati।

^n619 kathaṃ? pasādasaṅkhātaṃ pañcavidhampi ^b(ajjhattikarūpaṃ) nāma, itaraṃ ^b(bāhirarūpaṃ)।
^n620 pasādahadayasaṅkhātaṃ chabbidhampi ^b(vatthurūpaṃ) nāma, itaraṃ ^b(avatthurūpaṃ)।
^n621 pasādaviññattisaṅkhātaṃ sattavidhampi ^b(dvārarūpaṃ) nāma, itaraṃ advārarūpaṃ।
^n622 pasādabhāvajīvitasaṅkhātaṃ aṭṭhavidhampi ^b(indriyarūpaṃ) nāma, itaraṃ ^b(anindriyarūpaṃ)।
^n623 pasādavisayasaṅkhātaṃ dvādasavidhampi ^b(oḷārikarūpaṃ santikerūpaṃ, sappaṭigharūpañca,) itaraṃ ^b(sukhumarūpaṃ dūrerūpaṃ appaṭigharūpañca)।
^n624 kammajaṃ ^b(upādinnarūpaṃ,) itaraṃ ^b(anupādinnarūpaṃ)।
^n625 rūpa0āyatanaṃ ^b(sanidassanarūpaṃ,) itaraṃ ^b(anidassanarūpaṃ)।
^n626 cakkhādidvayaṃ asampattavasena, ghānādittayaṃ sampattavasenāti pañcavidhampi ^b(gocaraggāhikarūpaṃ,) itaraṃ ^b(agocaraggāhikarūpaṃ)।
^n627 vaṇṇo gandho raso ojā bhūtacatukkañceti aṭṭhavidhampi ^b(avinibbhogarūpaṃ,) itaraṃ ^b(vinibbhogarūpaṃ)।
^n628 iccevamaṭṭhavīsati-vidhampi ca vicakkhaṇā।
^n^sz ajjhattikādibhedena, vibhajanti yathārahaṃ॥
^n ^end ayamettha rūpavibhāgo।
rūpasamuṭṭhānanayo	^h(rūpasamuṭṭhānanayo)^n629 kammaṃ cittaṃ utu āhāro ceti ^b(cattāri rūpasamuṭṭhānāni) nāma।
^n630 tattha kāmāvacaraṃ rūpāvacarañceti pañcavīsatividhampi kusalākusalakammamabhisaṅkhataṃ ajjhattikasantāne kammasamuṭṭhānarūpaṃ paṭisandhimupādāya khaṇe khaṇe samuṭṭhāpeti।
^n631 arūpavipākadvipañcaviññāṇavajjitaṃ pañcasattatividhampi
 cittaṃ cittasamuṭṭhānarūpaṃ paṭhamabhavaṅgamupādāya jāyantameva samuṭṭhāpeti।
^n632 tattha appanājavanaṃ iriyāpathampi sannāmeti।
^n633 voṭṭhabbanakāmāvacarajavanābhiññā pana viññattimpi samuṭṭhāpenti।
^n634 somanassajavanāni panettha terasa hasanampi janenti।
^n635 sītuṇhotusamaññātā tejodhātu ṭhitippattāva utusamuṭṭhānarūpaṃ ajjhattañ0ca bahiddhā ca yathārahaṃ samuṭṭhāpeti।
^n636 ojāsaṅkhāto āhāro āhārasamuṭṭhānarūpaṃ ajjhoharaṇakāle ṭhānappattova samuṭṭhāpeti।
^n637 tattha hadayaindriyarūpāni kammajāneva।
^n638 viññattidvayaṃ cittajameva।
^n639 saddo cittotujo।
^n640 lahutādittayaṃ utucittāhārehi sambhoti।
^n641 avinibbhogarūpāni ceva ākāsadhātu ca। catūhi sambhūtāni।
^n642 lakkhaṇarūpāni na kutoci jāyanti।
^n643 aṭṭhārasa pannarasa, terasa dvādasā0ti ca।
^n^sz kammacittotukāhāra-jāni honti yathākkamaṃ॥
^n644 jāyamānādirūpānaṃ, sabhāvattā hi kevalaṃ।
^n^sz lakkhaṇāni na jāyanti, kehicīti pakāsitaṃ॥
^n ^end ayamettha rūpasamuṭṭhānanayo।
kalāpa	^h(kalāpayojanā)^n645 ekuppādā ekanirodhā ekanissayā sahavuttino ^b(ekavīsati rūpakalāpā) nāma।
^n646 tattha jīvitaṃ avinibbhogarūpañca cakkhunā saha cakkhudasakanti pavuccati।
 tathā sotādīhi saddhiṃ sotadasakaṃ ghānadasakaṃ jivhādasakaṃ kāyadasakaṃ itthibhāvadasakaṃ pumbhāvadasakaṃ vatthudasakañceti yathākkamaṃ yojetabbaṃ।
 avinibbhogarūpameva jīvitena saha jīvitanavakanti pavuccati।
 ime ^b(nava kammasamuṭṭhānakalāpā)।
^n647 avinibbhogarūpaṃ pana suddhaṭṭhakaṃ,
 tadeva kāyaviññattiyā saha kāyaviññattinavakaṃ,
 vacīviññattisaddehi saha vacīviññattidasakaṃ,
 lahutādīhi saddhiṃ lahutādekādasakaṃ,
 kāyaviññattilahutādidvādasakaṃ,
 vacīviññattisaddalahutāditerasakañceti
 ^b(cha cittasamuṭṭhānakalāpā)।
^n648 suddhaṭṭhakaṃ saddanavakaṃ lahutādekādasakaṃ saddalahutādidvādasakañceti ^b(cattāro utusamuṭṭhānakalāpā)।
^n649 suddhaṭṭhakaṃ lahutādekādasakañceti ^b(dveāhārasamuṭṭhānakalāpā)।
^n650 tattha suddhaṭṭhakaṃ saddanavakañceti dve utusamuṭṭhānakalāpā bahiddhāpi labbhanti,
 avasesā pana sabbe0pi ajjhattikamevāti।
^n651 kammacittotukāhāra-samuṭṭhānā yathākkamaṃ।
^n^sz nava cha caturo dveti, kalāpā ekavīsati॥
^n^sz kalāpānaṃ pariccheda-lakkhaṇattā vicakkhaṇā।
^n^sz na kalāpaṅgamiccāhu, ākāsaṃ lakkhaṇāni ca॥
^n ^end ayamettha kalāpayojanā।
rūpapavattikkamo	^h(rūpapavattikkamo)^n652 sabbānipi panetāni rūpāni kāmaloke yathārahaṃ anūnāni pavattiyaṃ upalabbhanti।
^n653 paṭisandhiyaṃ pana saṃsedajānañceva opapātikānañca cakkhusotaghānajivhākāyabhāvavatthudasakasaṅkhātāni satta dasakāni pātubhavanti ukkaṭṭhavasena,
 omakavasena pana cakkhusotaghānabhāvadasakāni kadācipi na labbhanti,
 tasmā tesaṃ vasena kalāpahāni veditabbā।
^n654 gabbhaseyyakasattānaṃ pana kāyabhāvavatthudasakasaṅkhātāni tīṇi dasakāni pātubhavanti,
 tatthāpi bhāvadasakaṃ kadāci na labbhati,
 tato paraṃ pavattikāle kamena cakkhudasakādīni ca pātubhavanti।
^n655 iccevaṃ paṭisandhimupādāya kammasamuṭṭhānā, dutiyacittamupādāya citta0samuṭṭhānā, ṭhitikālamupādāya utusamuṭṭhānā, ojāpharaṇamupādāya āhārasamuṭṭhānā ceti catusamuṭṭhānarūpakalāpasantati kāmaloke dīpajālā viya, nadīsoto viya ca yāvatāyukamabbocchinnā pavattati।
^n656 maraṇakāle pana cuticittoparisattarasamacittassa ṭhitikālamupādāya kammajarūpāni na uppajjanti,
 puretaramuppannāni ca kammajarūpāni cuticittasamakālameva pavattitvā nirujjhanti,
 tato paraṃ cittajāhārajarūpañca vocchijjati,
 tato paraṃ utusamuṭṭhānarūpaparamparā yāva matakaḷevarasaṅkhātā pavattanti।
^n657 iccevaṃ matasattānaṃ, puna0eva bhavantare।
^n^sz paṭisandhimupādāya, tathā rūpaṃ pavattati॥
rūpaloke	^n658 rūpaloke pana ghānajivhākāyabhāvadasakāni ca āhārajakalāpāni ca na labbhanti,
 tasmā tesaṃ paṭisandhikāle cakkhusotavatthuvasena tīṇi dasakāni jīvitanavakañceti cattāro kammasamuṭṭhānakalāpā,
 pavattiyaṃ cittotusamuṭṭhānā ca labbhanti।
^n659 asaññasattānaṃ pana cakkhusotavatthusaddāpi na labbhanti,
 tathā sabbānipi cittajarūpāni,
 tasmā tesaṃ paṭisandhikāle jīvitanavakameva,
 pavattiyañca saddavajjitaṃ utusamuṭṭhānarūpaṃ atiricchati।
^n660 iccevaṃ kāmarūpāsaññīsaṅkhātesu tīsu ṭhānesu paṭisandhipavattivasena duvidhā rūpappavatti veditabbā।
^n661 aṭṭha0vīsati kāmesu, honti tevīsa rūpisu।
^n^sz sattaraseva saññīnaṃ, arūpe natthi kiñci0pi॥
^n^sz saddo vikāro jaratā, maraṇañcopapattiyaṃ।
^n^sz na labbhanti pavatte tu, na kiñcipi na labbhati॥
^n ^end ayamettha rūpapavattikkamo।
nibbānabhedo	^h(nibbānabhedo)^n662 ^b(nibbānaṃ) pana lokuttarasaṅkhātaṃ catumaggañāṇena sacchikātabbaṃ
 maggaphalānamārammaṇabhūtaṃ vānasaṅkhātāya taṇhāya nikkhantattā nibbānanti pavuccati।
^n663 tadetaṃ sabhāvato ekavidhampi saupādisesanibbānadhātu anupādisesanibbānadhātu ceti duvidhaṃ hoti kāraṇapariyāyena।
^n664 tathā suññataṃ animittaṃ appaṇihitañceti tividhaṃ hoti ākārabhedena।
^n665^n700 padamaccutamaccantaṃ, asaṅkhatamanuttaraṃ।
^n^sz nibbānamiti bhāsanti, vānamuttā mahesayo॥
^n^sz iti cittaṃ cetasikaṃ, rūpaṃ nibbānamiccapi।
^n^sz paramatthaṃ pakāsenti, catudhāva tathāgatā॥
^n ^end iti abhidhammatthasaṅgahe rūpasaṅgahavibhāgo nāma
^n ^end chaṭṭho paricchedo।
samuccayaṃ	^ck#aas7(7. samuccayaparicchedo)^n701 dvāsattatividhā vuttā, vatthudhammā salakkhaṇā।
^n^sz tesaṃ dāni yathāyogaṃ, pavakkhāmi samuccayaṃ॥
^n702 akusalasaṅgaho
 missakasaṅgaho
 bodhipakkhiyasaṅgaho
 sabbasaṅgaho ceti
 samuccayasaṅgaho catubbidho veditabbo।
akusalasaṅgaho	^h(akusalasaṅgaho)^n703 kathaṃ? ^b(akusalasaṅgahe) tāva cattāro āsavā – kāma0āsavo bhava0āsavo diṭṭhāsavo avijjā2āsavo।
^n704 cattāro oghā – kāma0ogho bhava0ogho diṭṭhi1ogho avijjā1ogho।
^n705 cattāro yogā – kāma0yogo bhava0yogo diṭṭhi0yogo avijjā0yogo।
^n706 cattāro ganthā – abhijjhākāyagantho, byāpādo kāya0gantho, sīla0bata1parāmāso kāyagantho, idaṃ0sacca3abhiniveso kāyagantho।
^n707 cattāro upādānā – kāma0upādānaṃ diṭṭhi1upādānaṃ sīla0bata1upādānaṃ atta0vāda0upādānaṃ।
^n708 cha nīvaraṇāni – kāma2chanda0nīvaraṇaṃ byāpāda0nīvaraṇaṃ thina0middha0nīvaraṇaṃ
 uddhacca0kukkucca0nīvaraṇaṃ vicikicchā0nīvaraṇaṃ avijjānīvaraṇaṃ।
^n709 satta anusayā – kāma0rāga3anusayo bhava0rāga3anusayo paṭigha3anusayo
 māna3anusayo diṭṭhi0anusayo vicikicchā2anusayo avijjā2anusayo।
^n710 dasa saṃyojanāni – kāmarāgasaṃyojanaṃ rūparāgasaṃyojanaṃ arūparāgasaṃyojanaṃ paṭigha0saṃyojanaṃ
 māna0saṃyojanaṃ diṭṭhi0saṃyojanaṃ sīlabbataparāmāsasaṃyojanaṃ vicikicchā0saṃyojanaṃ uddhaccasaṃyojanaṃ avijjā0saṃyojanaṃ suttante।
^n711 aparāni0pi dasa saṃyojanāni – kāmarāgasaṃyojanaṃ bhava0rāga0saṃyojanaṃ paṭighasaṃyojanaṃ
 mānasaṃyojanaṃ diṭṭhisaṃyojanaṃ sīlabbataparāmāsasaṃyojanaṃ vicikicchāsaṃyojanaṃ issā0saṃyojanaṃ macchariya0saṃyojanaṃ avijjāsaṃyojanaṃ abhidhamme (^t@vb.969)।
^n712 dasa kilesā – lobho doso moho māno diṭṭhi vicikicchā thinaṃ uddhaccaṃ ahirikaṃ anottappaṃ।
^n713 āsavādīsu panettha kāmabhavanāmena tabbatthukā taṇhā adhippetā,
 sīlabbataparāmāso idaṃsaccābhiniveso attavādupādo ca tathāpavattaṃ diṭṭhigatameva pavuccati।
^n714 āsavoghā ca yogā ca,
^n^sz tayo ganthā ca vatthuto।
^n^sz upādānā duve vuttā,
^n^sz aṭṭha nīvaraṇā siyuṃ॥
^n^sz chaḷevānusayā honti, nava saṃyojanā matā।
^n^sz kilesā dasa vuttoyaṃ, navadhā pāpasaṅgaho॥
missakasaṅgaho	^h(missakasaṅgaho)^n715 ^b(missakasaṅgahe) cha hetū – lobho doso moho alobho adoso amoho।
^n716 satta jhānaṅgāni – vitakko vicāro pīti ekaggatā somanassaṃ domanassaṃ upekkhā।
^n717 dvādasa maggaṅgāni – sammā0diṭṭhi sammā0saṅkappo sammāvācā sammākammanto sammāājīvo sammā0vāyāmo
 sammā0sati sammā0samādhi micchādiṭṭhi micchā0saṅkappo micchā0vāyāmo micchā0samādhi।
^n718 bāvīsatindriyāni – cakkhu2indriyaṃ sota0indriyaṃ ghāna0indriyaṃ jivhā1indriyaṃ kāya0indriyaṃ itthi2indriyaṃ purisa0indriyaṃ jīvitindriyaṃ mano1indriyaṃ
 sukha0indriyaṃ dukkha0indriyaṃ somanassa0indriyaṃ domanassa0indriyaṃ upekkha0indriyaṃ saddha0indriyaṃ vīriya0indriyaṃ sati2indriyaṃ samādhi2indriyaṃ paññā1indriyaṃ
 anaññātañ0ñassāmī0ti2indriyaṃ aññā1indriyaṃ aññātāvi2indriyaṃ।
^n719 nava balāni – saddhā0balaṃ vīriya0balaṃ sati0balaṃ samādhi0balaṃ paññā0balaṃ hiri0balaṃ ottappa0balaṃ ahirikabalaṃ anottappabalaṃ।
^n720 cattāro adhipatī – chandādhipati vīriyādhipati cittādhipati vīmaṃsādhipati।
^n721 cattāro āhārā – kabaḷīkāro āhāro, phasso dutiyo, mano0sañcetanā tatiyā, viññāṇaṃ catutthaṃ।
^n722 indriyesu panettha sotāpattimaggañāṇaṃ anaññātaññassāmītindriyaṃ।
^n723 arahattaphalañāṇaṃ aññātāvindriyaṃ।
^n724 majjhe cha ñāṇāni aññindriyānīti pavuccanti।
^n725 jīvitindriyañca rūpārūpavasena duvidhaṃ hoti।
^n726 pañcaviññāṇesu jhānaṅgāni, avīriyesu balāni, ahetukesu maggaṅgāni na labbhanti।
^n727 tathā vicikicchācitte ekaggatā maggindriyabalabhāvaṃ na gacchati।
^n728 dvihetukatihetukajavanesveva yathāsambhavaṃ adhipati eko2eva labbhatīti।
^n729 cha hetū pañca jhānaṅgā, magga2aṅgā nava vatthuto।
^n^sz soḷasindriyadhammā ca, baladhammā naveritā॥
^n^sz cattārodhipati vuttā, tathāhārāti sattadhā।
