 buddhānussatiādīsu aṭṭhasu saññāvavatthānesu cāti dasasukammaṭṭhānesu upacārabhāvanāva sampajjati, natthi appanā।
^n920 sesesu pana samatiṃsakammaṭṭhānesu appanābhāvanāpi sampajjati।
^n921 tatthāpi dasa kasiṇāni ānāpānañca pañcakajjhānikāni।
^n922 dasa asubhā kāyagatāsati ca paṭhamajjhānikā।
^n923 mettādayo tayo catukkajjhānikā।
^n924 upekkhā pañcamajjhānikāti
